<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 09:17:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国刺激政策消退后欧洲股市下跌；关注美国CPI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-after-china-stimulus-excitement-wanes-focus-us-cpi-2024-12-10/</link><description>欧洲股市周二结束了连续八个交易日的上涨势头，受矿商股下跌的影响，中国刺激承诺引发的涨势在贸易数据疲软后逐渐减弱，而现在的焦点是美国通胀数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:29:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-after-china-stimulus-excitement-wanes-focus-us-cpi-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis与中国宁德时代将投资43.3亿美元在西班牙建设电动汽车电池工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chinas-catl-invest-433-bln-ev-battery-factory-spain-2024-12-10/</link><description>Stellantis 和中国电池制造商 CATL 在周二的一份声明中表示，将投资 41 亿欧元（43.3 亿美元）在西班牙北部萨拉戈萨建造一家电动汽车电池工厂。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chinas-catl-invest-433-bln-ev-battery-factory-spain-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国对俄罗斯出口四个月来首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-exports-russia-drop-first-time-four-months-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国海关周二公布的数据显示，11 月份中国对俄罗斯的人民币计价出口出现两位数下降，较 10 月份 24% 的增长大幅恶化，并且是四个月来首次下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-exports-russia-drop-first-time-four-months-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国宁德时代拟与Stellantis在西班牙成立价值40亿美元的电池合资公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-catl-plans-set-up-4-bln-battery-jv-spain-with-stellantis-2024-12-10/</link><description>根据宁德时代周二提交的股票文件，中国电动汽车巨头宁德时代计划与西班牙 Stellantis 成立一家电池合资企业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-catl-plans-set-up-4-bln-battery-jv-spain-with-stellantis-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋岛国等待特朗普，对气候和中国立场保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-islands-wait-trump-wary-climate-china-stance-2024-12-10/</link><description>外交官表示，太平洋岛国是美国和中国之间战略竞争的中心，这些国家带来了基础设施和资金，希望当选总统唐纳德·特朗普继续参与该地区事务，但担心竞争演变成对抗。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-islands-wait-trump-wary-climate-china-stance-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国因“干涉”香港事务而宣布对美国人员实施签证限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-announces-visa-restrictions-us-personnel-over-hong-kong-interference-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国外交部周二在新闻发布会上表示，中国决定对一些在涉港问题上“表现恶劣”、“干涉”香港事务的美国人员实施签证限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-announces-visa-restrictions-us-personnel-over-hong-kong-interference-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国准备进一步举债以对抗特朗普的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-ready-go-deeper-into-debt-counter-trumps-tariffs-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国领导人在十多年来最温和的声明之一中表示，他们准备采取一切必要的刺激措施，以应对美国预期的贸易关税对明年经济增长的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:43:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-ready-go-deeper-into-debt-counter-trumps-tariffs-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>星巴克任命首位中国首席增长官 - 媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-appoints-first-china-chief-growth-officer-media-2024-12-10/</link><description>据中国媒体《晚报》周二报道，星巴克中国任命了首位首席增长官（CGO）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-appoints-first-china-chief-growth-officer-media-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>贸易商称，中国恒力利用额外进口配额从道达尔购买中东石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-hengli-uses-extra-import-quota-buy-mideast-oil-total-traders-say-2024-12-10/</link><description>六名知情交易员表示，中国私营炼油商恒力石化已抢购中东原油，其中大部分来自法国石油巨头TotalEnergies，此前这家法国巨头囤积了大量石油，且伊朗对中国的供应收紧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 06:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-hengli-uses-extra-import-quota-buy-mideast-oil-total-traders-say-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>阿萨德倒台暴露中国中东外交局限性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/assads-fall-syria-exposes-limits-chinas-middle-east-diplomacy-2024-12-10/</link><description>阿萨德政权的垮台对中国的全球野心是一个打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/assads-fall-syria-exposes-limits-chinas-middle-east-diplomacy-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>习近平表示，中国对实现今年经济增长目标充满信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-has-full-confidence-achieving-this-years-growth-target-says-xi-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周二表示，中国对实现今年经济增长目标、继续发挥世界经济增长第一引擎作用充满信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-has-full-confidence-achieving-this-years-growth-target-says-xi-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国政策讨论提振股市，但债券受阻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-10/</link><description>汤姆·威斯布鲁克 (Tom Westbrook) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国半程马拉松奖品为牛、野生鱼和鸡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-half-marathon-offers-cow-wild-fish-chickens-prizes-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国东北吉林省的一场半程马拉松宣布了不同寻常的奖品选择，第一名冲线的选手赢得一头牛，其他参赛者获得野生鱼、鹅或公鸡，以吸引更多参与者并推广当地农产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-half-marathon-offers-cow-wild-fish-chickens-prizes-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>电池制造商的帮助将维持锂供应过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-supply-surplus-set-stay-with-battery-makers-help-2024-12-10/</link><description>以中国运营商为首的许多锂矿仍在维持电动汽车（EV）电池所需原材料的生产，无视价格疲软足以引发大规模减产的情况，这为电池制造商带来了福音。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 04:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-supply-surplus-set-stay-with-battery-makers-help-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>查看特朗普关税前中国11月出口增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-november-export-growth-slows-ahead-trump-tariffs-2024-12-10/</link><description>11月份中国出口增速较上月放缓，而进口则萎缩，这表明随着美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫带来新的贸易风险，人们对这个世界第二大经济体感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-november-export-growth-slows-ahead-trump-tariffs-2024-12-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>